'''Google Pay'''是[[Google|Google]]的[[行動支付|行動支付]]服務，儲存於Google帳戶內的支付資訊將整合到各項Google產品服務中而更方便交易或進行非接觸式付款和網路購物。

截至2018年1月8日，Google Wallet 和 Android Pay 已整合為一個名為 Google Pay 的單一行動支付服務(Pay with Google)。

Google Wallet是Google較早發展的支付工具，可用於實體及網路消費付款以及個人之間的交易，後來推出了全球通行的Android Pay，則調整為個人間的收付、轉帳功能，而且連結美國銀行帳戶而以美國市場為主。<ref name="#1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/google-launches-google-pay-mobile-payment-service/|title=Google merges payment platforms under Google Pay brand|last=Nieva|first=Richard|date=8 January 2018|work=[[CNET|CNET]]|access-date=8 January 2018|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|last2=Bennett|first2=Brian|archive-date=2018-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108185621/https://www.cnet.com/news/google-launches-google-pay-mobile-payment-service/|dead-url=no}}</ref>Android Pay更名並重新命名為Google Pay。Google Pay將擁有Android Pay的所有功能，而Google Wallet功能（例如請求和發送資金）將出現在[[Google_Pay_Send|Google Pay Send]]中，該功能目前是一個單獨的應用程序。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2018/01/google-rebrands-all-its-payment-solutions-as-google-pay/|title=Google rebrands all its payment solutions as “Google Pay”|last=Amadeo|first=Ron|date=8 January 2018|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|access-date=8 January 2018|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108181110/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2018/01/google-rebrands-all-its-payment-solutions-as-google-pay/|archivedate=2018-01-08|df=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/google-launches-google-pay-mobile-payment-service/|title=Google merges payment platforms under Google Pay brand|last=Nieva|first=Richard|date=8 January 2018|work=[[CNET|CNET]]|access-date=8 January 2018|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|last2=Bennett|first2=Brian|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108185621/https://www.cnet.com/news/google-launches-google-pay-mobile-payment-service/|archivedate=2018-01-08|df=}}</ref>

更名服務提供了一個新的API，允許商家將支付服務添加到網站、應用程序、[[Stripe|Stripe]]、[[Braintree|Braintree]]和[[Google_Assistant|Google Assistant]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/05/17/google-will-now-let-users-pay-with-any-card-they-have-on-file-not-just-those-saved-in-android-pay/|title=Google will now let users pay with any card they have on file, not just those saved in Android Pay|last=Perez|first=Sarah|date=17 May 2017|work=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|access-date=24 December 2017|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225092307/https://techcrunch.com/2017/05/17/google-will-now-let-users-pay-with-any-card-they-have-on-file-not-just-those-saved-in-android-pay/|archivedate=2017-12-25|df=}}</ref>。該服務允許用戶使用他們在Google Play上儲存的支付卡<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://9to5google.com/2017/10/23/pay-with-google-online-payments/|title=‘Pay with Google’ makes it easy to pay online with any card tied to your Google account|last=Schoon|first=Ben|date=23 October 2017|work=9to5Google|access-date=24 December 2017|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225203129/https://9to5google.com/2017/10/23/pay-with-google-online-payments/|archivedate=2017-12-25|df=}}</ref>。

2018年5月，Google Pay應用程序還增加了對登機證和活動門票的支持。<br>
