'''Google Wallet'''（'''Google電子錢包'''）允許使用者從行動裝置或桌上型電腦向寄件人或收件人免費發送和接收款項。設定後，Google電子錢包帳戶必須與美國或英國的現有借記卡或銀行帳戶相關聯。<ref>{{cite web|title=Set up Wallet|url=https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285508?hl=en&ref_topic=6285490|publisher=Google|accessdate=18 October 2017|archive-date=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506190904/https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285508?hl=en&ref_topic=6285490|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Google Wallet|url = https://www.google.com/wallet/faq/|publisher = Google|access-date = 2016-02-08|archive-date = 2018-01-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180125200318/http://www.google.com/wallet/faq/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Your Wallet Card - Wallet Help|url = https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285510?hl=en|publisher = Google|access-date = 2016-07-21|archive-date = 2016-10-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161005175118/https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285510?hl=en|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>

實際的Google Wallet Card是該應用的一項可選附加功能，允許使用者透過Gmail附件匯款，附加的借記卡帳戶或銀行帳戶中的資金在銷售點進行購買，這張卡還可以用來在自動取款機上提取現金，不收取Google相關費用，實際上可以用作借記卡，包括租車等。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Add a bank account - Wallet Help|url = https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285491?hl=en&ref_topic=6285490|publisher = Google|access-date = 2016-02-08|archive-date = 2016-05-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160506190946/https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285491?hl=en&ref_topic=6285490|dead-url = no}}</ref>

Google Wallet的結構允許其顧客互相匯款，Google Wallet使用者可以輸入收件人的電子郵件地址或電話號碼，接收者必須將該電話號碼或電子郵件地址連結至銀行帳戶才能存取這些資金，如果收件人也有Google Wallet帳戶，資金將直接過帳到該帳戶，當創建電子錢包帳戶時，使用者最多可以連結兩個銀行帳戶，收到的錢將轉到Google Wallet餘額，並保留在該電子錢包餘額中，直到使用者決定將其兌換為關聯的帳戶，或者使用Google Wallet Card直接從該帳戶支出。<ref name="support.google.com">{{Cite web|title = Set up your Wallet app - Wallet Help|url = https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285508?hl=en&ref_topic=6285490|publisher = Google|access-date = 2016-02-08|archive-date = 2016-05-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160506190904/https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285508?hl=en&ref_topic=6285490|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Welcome to a new Google Wallet|url = http://googlecommerce.blogspot.com/2015/09/new-google-wallet.html|website = Google Commerce|access-date = 2016-02-08|archive-date = 2016-08-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160828193422/https://googlecommerce.blogspot.com/2015/09/new-google-wallet.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/parmyolson/2017/09/18/google-mobile-wallet-india-tez/|title=Google Pitches A Mobile Wallet To India's 300 Million Smartphone Users|last=Olson|first=Parmy|work=Forbes|access-date=2017-09-22|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126162814/https://www.forbes.com/sites/parmyolson/2017/09/18/google-mobile-wallet-india-tez/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#3">{{Cite news|url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/09/17/google-debuts-tez-a-mobile-wallet-and-payments-app-for-india/|title=Google debuts Tez, a mobile payments app for India that uses Audio QR to transfer money|last=Lunden|first=Ingrid|work=TechCrunch|access-date=2017-09-22|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124130243/https://techcrunch.com/2017/09/17/google-debuts-tez-a-mobile-wallet-and-payments-app-for-india/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Google不會向使用者存取Google Wallet收取費用，發送和接收資金是免費的，正如透過關聯的銀行賬戶向錢包卡添加資金一樣，使用者可以向電子錢包餘額中添加多少錢，從關聯的帳戶或卡上退出，或者發送和接收給其他人都有限制，這些限制是針對每筆交易以及在特定時間段內設定的，以前，透過借記卡添加的資金需要支付2.9%的費用，但Google從2016年5月2日起放棄了這一能力。<ref name="ReferenceA">{{Cite web|title = Fees, limits & transfer times - Wallet Help|url = https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285486?hl=en|publisher = Google|access-date = 2016-04-16|archive-date = 2016-10-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161017043424/https://support.google.com/wallet/answer/6285486?hl=en|dead-url = no}}</ref>

